    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a lid with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half </strong>the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for 1-2 min or until golden</p><p>Once golden, add a little <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>relish </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), mix to combine then transfer to a bowl and set aside, reserve the pot – this is your <strong>garlic & chilli oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1711453855790-x200.jpg",
