            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe the reserved pot clean and return it to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>leek</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[900ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L] </span><strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
