      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> to a <strong>tin</strong> <strong>foil</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray under the grill for an initial 1-2 min or until beginning to brown</p><p>Once browned, remove the tray from the grill and top with the <strong>remaining chilli relish</strong>, <strong>crumbled goats' cheese</strong> and <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheddar</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the grill for a further 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted – these are your <strong>chilli jam & goats' cheese toasts</strong></p>",
